        <p class="text-sm text-primary-400 mb-6 flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 mr-1.5 text-primary-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
          Sąd Rejonowy dla Warszawy-Mokotowa w Warszawie
